  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Requesting and sending amount with decimals higher than 18 using a scientific format doesn’t show «Max number of decimals is 18».\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nWarning «Max number of decimals is 18».\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nTransaction request is sent.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Login\r\n- Open a chat\r\n- Send `/request ETH 5e-23434554546645245`\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Status version 0.9.28\r\n* Operating System: Android\r\n![2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/42981338/45060293-991e7980-b09f-11e8-8d4a-577813ebb591.png)\r\n",
